headline: Filterbaby Announces Nationwide Retail Expansion into Target
summary: Filterbaby, the award-winning skincare water filtration brand and leader in dermatologist-recommended water filters, today announces its national retail debut at Target. Filterbaby's new Essential Collection is now shoppable in a full chainwide rollout to more than 1,800 Target stores and on Target.com.
